#include<iostream>
#include<cstdio>
#include<string>
#include<utility>
#include<map>
#include<algorithm>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
    map<string ,int>map1;
    map1["JAN"]=1;map1["FEB"]=2;map1["MAR"]=3;map1["APR"]=4;map1["MAY"]=5;map1["JUN"]=6;
    map1["JUL"]=7;map1["AUG"]=8;map1["SEP"]=9;map1["OCT"]=10;map1["NOV"]=11;map1["DEC"]=12;
    int t;
    scanf("%d",&t);
    for(int k=1;k<=t;k++)
    {
        string s;
        cin>>s;
        int day,month,year,isleap=0,days=0;
        int m[13]={0,31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
        string temp;
        temp=s.substr(0,2);
        day=((int(temp[0])-48)*10)+(int(temp[1])-48);
        temp=s.substr(3,3);
        month=map1[temp];
        temp=s.substr(7,4);
        year=((int(temp[0])-48)*1000)+((int(temp[1])-48)*100)+((int(temp[2])-48)*10)+(int(temp[3])-48);
        //cout<<day<<endl<<month<<endl<<year<<endl;
        if((year%4==0 && year%100!=0)|(year%400==0))
            isleap=1;
        if(isleap==1)
            m[2]=29;
        for(int i=1;i<=month-1;i++)
            days+=m[i];
        days+=day;
        if(days<=300)
            cout<<"Case "<<k<<": "<<days<<" Hundreds\n";
        else if(days>300 && days<=360)
            cout<<"Case "<<k<<": "<<days-300<<" Tens\n";
        else if(days>360)
            cout<<"Case "<<k<<": "<<days-360<<" Ones\n";
    }
    return 0;
}
